public abstract class AContentTypeEdition
extends TypicalWindow
implements IDetailPanel, ILocalizedNamesReceiver

Abstract base class for Content Types edition panels. Concrete logic for "accept" buttons (create new/edit) is implemented in subclasses.

Author:
Andrei Cojocaru, Manuel Ruiz
